@startuml
title AttendanceRecord Class Diagram - School Management System

hide circle

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ClassBorderColor #334155
skinparam ClassBackgroundColor white
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FEF9C3
skinparam NoteBorderColor #A16207

class AttendanceRecord {
  -id: bigint
  -class_id: bigint
  -student_id: bigint
  -attendance_date: date
  -status: enum
  -grade: integer
  -feedback: text

  --
  +courseClass(): BelongsTo
  +student(): BelongsTo
}

note right of AttendanceRecord
AttendanceRecord stores a student's
attendance status for a specific
class group and date.

It can also include a grade and
feedback related to the session.
end note

@enduml